title: CANT UPDATE 5.11
body:
at 11% the update speed dropped to 0KBps and a error came up >.<
pls help, i wanna ranked

replies.body: In addition to what Agent Mindstar said, you might want to venture over [here](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664#wq5) and experiment with using a different DNS.

Hey,

If you haven't already - have a look through the [patching issues](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/202969434-Patching-Issues) article on support.riotgames.com and see if the suggestions there help out!

-Mindstar
